snippet.title: BattleCakes - Steam Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
BattleCakes is coming to Steam on October 26th, 2023! 

Explore Pasteleria and solve the mystery of missing King Feliz as you shape your adventure by choosing to battle or befriend the critters you encounter along the way. Discover the joy of friendship and community as you fight to leave the world better off than you found it and make your mark.

Wishlist here: BattleCakes.com/Wishlist
